Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:05.02,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Hear ye, hear ye!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.02,0:00:08.44,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,This meeting of the Cutie Mark Crusaders is now in session!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:09.78,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Who wants to do roll-call?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:13.20,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure we're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:15.85,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Apple Bloom, what's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.85,0:00:17.62,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:23.04,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Except this letter from Babs Seed saying she's got her cutiemark!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:24.19,Somepony,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:26.36,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,She says it's a pair of scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.36,0:00:29.09,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,So… she's gotta cutting stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.09,0:00:30.50,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:33.09,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,She was always fussing with her bangs and tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:35.78,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I bet she'll grows up to be a celebrity stylist!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.78,0:00:38.69,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,But, if she spends all her time cutting hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.69,0:00:41.27,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,who's gotta run the Manehatten CMCs?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:42.45,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Well, not Babs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.45,0:00:46.12,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,She can't be a Cutie Mark Crusader if she's already got her cutie-mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.12,0:00:47.97,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Oh, well! I guess, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:50.95,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I'm glad she's happy, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:54.18,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I sure wouldn't want to be up to my flank in mane hair all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:57.29,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Can you imagine getting stuck with a cutie-mark you didn't like?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.45,0:00:59.48,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.48,0:01:01.54,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Or, at least, I hadn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:02.92,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:05.52,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Most of your family have apple-related cutie-marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.52,0:01:06.92,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I bet yours will be too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:08.89,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,And what's not to like about apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.89,0:01:11.38,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,There's the core, and sour apples,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:14.30,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,and rotten apples, and apples with worms in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:16.35,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.35,0:01:17.64,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Not helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.70,0:02:03.53,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I guess I just spent so much time worryin' about how to get a cutie mark,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:06.31,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I never even thought about what would happen after!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:08.68,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,There's just so many things I never considered!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.91,0:02:11.84,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there are, but you don't need to…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:14.55,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What if I finally get my cutie mark and I don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.55,0:02:17.02,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What if I get my cutie mark and nopony likes me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:18.27,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, that's just ridicu…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.27,0:02:20.19,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What if the Crusaders drift apart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:23.24,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I mean, we won't really be the Cutie Mark Crusaders anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:25.98,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What if it's non-apple?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:27.26,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Will I have to move out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:28.39,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Where will I live?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:30.70,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,All right, that's enough, sugarcube.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:34.04,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Those are way too many questions to answer them all in one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:34.40,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:37.10,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And nopony's gonna make you move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:39.19,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.19,0:02:40.93,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:42.39,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Now get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:45.33,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You'll see. Everything will be better in the mornin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:50.01,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Hush now, little sister \N You're loved by all you know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:53.96,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You'll never lose their friendship \N No matter where you go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:58.45,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,There ain't no call to worry \N So don't you cry or fret
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:03:02.84,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,A cutie mark won't change you \N No matter what you get
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:09.34,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,No matter, what I get.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:27.26,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Nothing like a good night's sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:28.29,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:32.74,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,You were right, Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:34.52,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I feel much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:37.20,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I was so worried about last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.07,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,See? Now what did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:41.15,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,A good night's sleep will fix just about it…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:45.49,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, no wonder you were so worked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:47.09,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:48.05,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.05,0:03:50.87,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Looks like somepony got her cutiemark!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:53.98,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:55.87,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I got my cutiemark!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:03:59.00,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I got my cutiemark!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:02.38,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I got my cutiemark!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:08.73,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Wait till I'll tell the others that my cutie-mark is a…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:11.89,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:14.54,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:16.65,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I know what it means!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:23.61,Somepony,,0,0,0,,It means I can retire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.36,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Infestations?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:31.39,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,You mean, like parasprites?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:35.80,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Please, anypony with a trombone can get rid of parasprites.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:38.22,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about the serious stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:40.99,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You ever hear of… twittermites?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:44.74,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Twittermites?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:52.79,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Pest ponies like you and me are the only thing that's keeping these live wires from destroying half of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.05,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Pest ponies?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:56.01,Somepony,,0,0,0,,That's no easy trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.01,0:05:01.81,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Even the best of us earn for the day they can move on to greener pastures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:06.29,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oh, now that you're here to take over my day has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:07.70,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Take over?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:12.31,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You gonna need to stop repeating everything I said and pay attention if you wanna learn anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:13.40,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:15.77,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I guess, this just wasn't what I was expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:17.83,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Ah, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:21.31,Somepony,,0,0,0,,With the cutiemark like that I'm sure you got the touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:22.29,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,The touch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:23.15,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:29.71,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Now, here you're gonna be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.02,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Once these things get out,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.02,0:05:34.57,Somepony,,0,0,0,,it can be pret-ty shocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:39.56,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:41.07,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:43.38,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oh, told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:47.33,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And the further apart they spread, the more powerful these bolts will get.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:51.65,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:53.20,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You call them back, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:56.08,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Twittermites!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:07.17,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Twittermites!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:16.77,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Bug, bug, bug, bug, bug, bug, bu-u-ug!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:23.77,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like you're all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:27.77,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Drop me a note sometime at the Piney Shade Retirement Community.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:28.99,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Now, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:31.87,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I'm sure this job is real important, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:34.98,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I don't think I wanna call bugs for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:37.41,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Hey, where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:38.87,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Well, well, well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:41.81,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Look at the new bug pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:43.47,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,It's pest pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:47.55,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,Ew, it sure is! Ew!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:51.97,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,I might've known you'd end up with the worst cutie mark ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:58.19,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,But look on the bright side!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:02.67,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,Whenever you need a friend, you can just go out and catch one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:04.20,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,That's not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:07.38,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Heeere, friendfriendfriendfriendfrieeend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:08.71,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:10.75,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,Here bug, here bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:12.31,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,Will you be my friend, bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:14.83,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,Because nopony else will!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:16.33,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:19.55,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,My cutie mark isn't the worst, you two are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:33.68,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I'd hate to think that Diamond Tiara is right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:37.32,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,But this cutie mark sure isn't what I was hoping for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:40.51,Shadow,,0,0,0,,Why should you have to keep it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:42.13,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.89,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:51.31,Shadow,,0,0,0,,If your cutie mark bothers you so much, get rid of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:57.53,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Well if you know how to wave a hoof and erase a terrible cutie mark, you go right ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:08:00.43,Shadow,,0,0,0,,As easily said as done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:09.13,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Huh. Now that is some serious magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:17.64,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where's everypony goin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:24.01,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Mayor! What's goin' on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.01,0:08:27.19,Mayor,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom, you've got to get your family out of town!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:33.24,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Twittermites!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:43.29,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Twittermites!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:46.96,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Here, bugbugbugbugbugbug!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:51.81,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Here, bugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:01.60,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Come on, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:05.79,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom! What in tarnation are you doin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:09.11,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I'm tryin' to stop the infestation, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:11.45,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Only a pest pony can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:17.20,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Now come on! We gotta skedaddle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:22.06,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,But I've gotta do somethin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:23.95,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Are you crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:51.19,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Whoo-ee. That's what I call a nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.73,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,, It seemed so real!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:54.27,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:10:00.65,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Applejack! You are not gonna believe the dream I just had!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:03.09,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I guess I needed more sleep than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:04.91,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,See, now what did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.29,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,A good night's sleep'll fix just about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.99,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, no wonder you were so worked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:11.75,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:14.84,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Looks like somepony got her cutie mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.13,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.35,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I mean... I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.23,0:10:23.45,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Potion making! Now that's more like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:25.21,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,More like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:26.23,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:29.57,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad Princess Twilight's lessons finally paid off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:34.11,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I expect you'll want to run off to the clubhouse and tell your friends all about your new cutie mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:37.20,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But before you go, make sure you do all your...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:40.53,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,chores?..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:47.47,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Why all the excitement?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:49.45,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:52.13,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:55.63,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,except this brand new cutie mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:57.55,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.55,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:00.01,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:02.60,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose either of you got yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.60,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.17,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Me neither...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:09.26,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I know it's silly but I'd always hoped we'd get our cutie marks together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:10.58,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:12.75,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,But I'm still super excited for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:14.31,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.45,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:18.46,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Let's call this meeting to order!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:22.65,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the three of us can figure out how to get two more cutie marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:25.19,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Um, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:26.74,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:27.50,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:30.52,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Well, you can't be a Cutie Mark Crusader
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:33.54,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,if you've already got your cutie mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:35.27,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.02,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Just like Babs Seed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:41.09,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Well, I could just sit quietly in the corner while you two figure out what you're gonna do...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:45.23,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Well, technically the clubhouse is for Crusaders only.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:47.47,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Oh. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:50.74,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I guess I should just come back later, then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:51.56,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:54.19,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I mean, you can't come in then either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:56.48,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Rules are rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:12:00.03,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,I don't even think we're still supposed to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:01.25,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.92,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:09.44,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Scootaloo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:12.10,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Come on, fillies, this isn't funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:18.07,Shadow,,0,0,0,,More trouble with cutie marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:19.74,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:21.68,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I mean… yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:22.93,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:24.71,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Well, I've gotten mine, but
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:28.31,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,my friends didn't get theirs, and now there's all kinds of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:35.32,Shadow,,0,0,0,,Sounds to me like cutie marks and trouble are two peas in the same pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:36.78,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:40.98,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I mean, if I was a blank flank again, there wouldn't be a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:44.00,Shadow,,0,0,0,,Your wish is my command.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:52.92,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Hey Applebloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:54.57,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Why did you wanna meet here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:59.19,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Well, us blank flanks have to meet somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:01.67,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Um, actually, Applebloom,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:04.62,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,we both sorta got our cutiemarks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:05.83,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:08.35,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:11.78,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Oh, we don't have time to go into all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:14.89,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,And we certainly don't have time to hang out in an old clubhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:17.42,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We've got responsibilities now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:19.25,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,But... maybe we'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:20.54,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Much later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:21.32,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:22.03,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:23.83,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I can get my cutiemark back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:24.84,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:27.57,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I mean, I got it once, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.85,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Just wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:34.58,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Noooo!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:45.84,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What in Equestria is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:47.36,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:52.14,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure sleep is the cure-all Applejack thinks it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:55.74,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.74,0:13:59.19,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I know you said sleep is supposed to make me feel better, but
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:02.09,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure it's making me feel worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:03.97,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,See? Now what did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.97,0:14:05.81,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,A good night sleep will fix…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:09.50,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, no wonder you were so worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:10.38,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:12.01,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear what I've said?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:12.94,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I was trying to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:14.51,Granny Smith,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:16.96,Granny Smith,,0,0,0,,What do we have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.13,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What is it, Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:19.21,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:20.99,Granny Smith,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:22.70,Granny Smith,,0,0,0,,Right, Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:23.88,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:25.48,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:27.17,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Right, Big Mac?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:30.71,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Truth is, Apple Bloom,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:33.00,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,it's your cutiemark.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:34.45,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Eyeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:35.57,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:37.13,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:44.11,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll tell you what it ain't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:46.09,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,It ain't no apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:47.71,Granny Smith,,0,0,0,,N-nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:48.60,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:52.97,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,And we don't have room for non-apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.18,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,N-nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:56.37,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Time for you to mosey on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:58.14,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,You can't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:00.26,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,But this is my home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:05.58,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Oh, and you're gonna have to change your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:07.80,Granny Smith,,0,0,0,,Eyeup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:11.45,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,I think just 'Bloom' has a nice ring to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:13.45,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Don't you, Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:14.39,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Eyeup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:22.73,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Noooo!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.35,0:15:32.30,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Allright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:35.27,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,This is getting ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:47.93,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd be so happy to not get a cutiemark!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:48.97,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What the…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:02.82,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna see another cutiemark as long as I live!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:09.88,Shadow,,0,0,0,,Back so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.39,0:16:12.19,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,All right, whoever you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:14.75,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I dunno what spell you went and cast on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:17.56,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,but I want it to stop right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:22.06,Shadow,,0,0,0,,I didn't cast a spell on you or anypony else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.28,0:16:24.69,Shadow,,0,0,0,,I only did what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:30.22,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Why would I want you to torement me with nightmares?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:33.33,Shadow,,0,0,0,,You, didn't want to catch bugs and I helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:36.71,Shadow,,0,0,0,,You didn't want to lose friends and I helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:39.55,Shadow,,0,0,0,,If there's a problem with your family,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.55,0:16:42.46,Shadow,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I can help with that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:44.54,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I don't want your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:46.33,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Just get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:48.86,Luna,,0,0,0,,Oh, Applebloom,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:51.40,Luna,,0,0,0,,you can't get away from your own shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:01.65,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:03.73,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,My shadow? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:13.70,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,It's just me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:16.54,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,You mean I've been doing all of that to myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:18.29,Luna,,0,0,0,,Of course, Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:19.93,Luna,,0,0,0,,It's your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:23.65,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,If I've been dreaming this whole time, why wouldn't I just wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:30.14,Luna,,0,0,0,,Sometimes we can worry about a thing so much that fear can make us feel like we're trapped in a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:39.21,Luna,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose there's anything you're particularly afraid of, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:41.00,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:44.20,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm pretty worried about getting my cutiemark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:48.01,Luna,,0,0,0,,Well, that is the same as worrying about who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:50.08,Luna,,0,0,0,,That is all a cutiemark is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:52.37,Luna,,0,0,0,,If you cannot accept who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:55.48,Luna,,0,0,0,,your life might seem like a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:58.12,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,But if I like who I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:00.53,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,do you think other ponies will too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:02.77,Luna,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:07.28,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Then it doesn't matter what my cutiemark is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:08.68,Luna,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.68,0:18:10.51,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,But that's so simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.51,0:18:14.98,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I must be the only pony in the universe that's worried about her cutiemark.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:18.02,Luna,,0,0,0,,Oh, I wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:19.64,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Scootaloo and Sweetie Belle are havin' nightmares too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:21.91,Luna,,0,0,0,,It's been a busy night for us all,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:25.24,Luna,,0,0,0,,but I think it's time to bring it to a close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:32.52,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:35.25,Luna,,0,0,0,,I know you've all had a lot on your minds tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:39.83,Luna,,0,0,0,,but I think Apple Bloom has something she'd like to share before you wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:41.83,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,We're still asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:43.16,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:47.58,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:52.67,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I guess I should call this dream meeting of the Cutie Mark Crusaders to order.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:57.33,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I know we all got pretty anxious when we found out Babs got her cutiemark,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.33,0:20:01.90,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,but I for one don't want to have nightmares every night from now 'til we get ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:03.15,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:05.16,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And even though we're all a little scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:09.09,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,a cutiemark won't change who you are or how everypony feels about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.09,0:20:11.71,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,It's lucky we're all scared of the same things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:15.37,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,That way we can help and remind each other to just be who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:18.81,Luna,,0,0,0,,And when the day comes that you all finally get your cutiemarks,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:21.36,Luna,,0,0,0,,you can be sure they'll fit you to a T.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:23.00,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:26.96,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Do you fillies think that Babs is worried or scared about some of this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:30.92,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I know! Let's put together a care package for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:33.25,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,That way she will know she isn't alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:38.75,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't want her to think that just because she isn't a Crusader, we can't still be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:40.44,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,But, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:43.14,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,maybe we should wait 'til we wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:44.20,Luna,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:06.16,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,There ain't no call to worry \N So don't you cry or fret
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:10.72,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,A cutie mark won't change me \N No matter what I get
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:14.19,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, sure looks like somepony's feelin' better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:17.27,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,You have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:19.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,See, now what did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:23.01,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,A good night's sleep cures just about everythin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:24.93,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:28.43,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I just wish it hadn't been so exhaustin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:36.73,Somepony,,0,0,0,,СЧАСТЛИВЫЙ ПОНЕЦ
